entries.femaleVariant: Heh, goddam walkin' in three directions at once, heheh, weapons goin' off every time theirs did.
Down in Mexico, corpocunts jacked me up and the other guys together, yeah? Linked up, like, 'n'…?
Heh, know what that makes me? A  supercorpse, man, I'm a fuckin' supercorpse!
Supercorpse, super dismissed, yeah? Then sayonara, amigo. Heh, served with honor! Served with honor, did ya?
Well, wiped it outta my head… Weren't no trainin', that, nuh-uh. Nope, nuh-uh… not no trainin', that… not no trainin'!
Felt what they felt, hits they took. Fuckin' pain, ten, a hundred times what I could take.
Then those guys died, an' I died, I died with 'em. In there with each of them, yeah? Inside their heads…
Fucked my head time after time… And then - outta nowhere, they said you're done, yeah? "Diiiiis-missed!"
